  "body": "Hi,\n\nAs noted in bug fsnotify/fsnotify#130, fsnotify fails to work correctly (or at all) in arm64, ppc64 and ppc64el.\n\nThis was preventing prometheus to be accepted in Debian testing, so while this is solved upstream, I hacked together a [patch](http://anonscm.debian.org/cgit/pkg-go/packages/prometheus.git/tree/debian/patches/07-Disable_fsnotify.patch) to disable fsnotify and rely only on refresh intervals in those architectures. You might want to consider applying something similar, so prom keeps working.\n",
